title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Justin Gaard/Dan Hayes/Matt Birk
description: JG joins the show to add some context to all the news about the Big 10 possibly resuming the 2020-21 college football season.  Dan Hayes calls in to talk about the Twins bounce back win last night.  Plus, the weekly Birk bit with Matt Birk!
